    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723770/extras/c7284b4c649e51d450bcc145fca534c2.poster.avif?t=1768466893\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723770/extras/c7284b4c649e51d450bcc145fca534c2.webm?t=1768466893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723770/extras/c7284b4c649e51d450bcc145fca534c2.mp4?t=1768466893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位年轻的博主Arina Demidova前往阿尔泰共和国为她的订户创造新材料。 对发现的渴望和探索周围世界的渴望将导致一个神圣的秘密，将改变她在这次旅程中的整个命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女孩博客决定去寻找阿尔泰山脉境内的阿拉特尔王国失落的城市，为订阅者提供关于它的新的迷人报道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，命运正在为她完全不同的转折做准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723770/extras/83cd533c0f242ec139cf81a0681e77fa.poster.avif?t=1768466893\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723770/extras/83cd533c0f242ec139cf81a0681e77fa.webm?t=1768466893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723770/extras/83cd533c0f242ec139cf81a0681e77fa.mp4?t=1768466893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >设置</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个致力于阿尔泰共和国土着人民的文化、神话和日常生活的冒险探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在每个人都有机会沉浸在这个神秘地区的文化中，足不出户参观神圣的地方并参加古老的仪式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特征</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸于阿尔泰地区独特的文化与传统；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融合寻物解谜、解谜解谜、迷你游戏、探索周边世界的精彩游戏体验；</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723770/extras/ef8bb5a1cffb39e1aa9a4004b149b6b9.poster.avif?t=1768466893\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723770/extras/ef8bb5a1cffb39e1aa9a4004b149b6b9.webm?t=1768466893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723770/extras/ef8bb5a1cffb39e1aa9a4004b149b6b9.mp4?t=1768466893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本项目由阿尔泰共和国旅游部科学顾问团队及著名阿尔泰音乐家多布林·萨廷共同参与创作，后者为游戏角色设计了形象并献声；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操控两位拥有不同任务的游戏角色；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引人入胜的剧情，沉浸式虚拟旅游体验。</p></li></ul>",
